{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43886-sinha-ra-kharayo","title":"सिंह र खरायो","description":"यो किताप भर्खर सावाँअक्षर मात्र पढ्‌न सक्ने भएका साना साना नानीहरूका लागि सरल भाषामा पुनर्लेखन गरिएको हो । यस किताबमा चतुर खरायोले जङ्गलको राजा सिंहलाई छक्याएको रमाइलो कथा छ ।","language":"Nepali","langCode":"ne","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Room to Read Literacy Program"],"illustrators":["Promina Shreshtha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43886-sinha-ra-kharayo"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99630/size3/e4e0b6c0f880dd0b5a8ee9ac904202f2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/99630/size6/e4e0b6c0f880dd0b5a8ee9ac904202f2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81406/size6/c44ce45a76a6c7c2b7ad0fb642dea094.jpg","text":"एउटा ठूलो वन थियो । सिंह वनको राजा थियो ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81407/size6/db7c889dc22d3a59597274eb7bf9695d.jpg","text":"वनमा बाघ, भालु, हात्ती, खरायो बस्थे ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81408/size6/2447df007cc8e1c940a1a353d2762a08.jpg","text":"सिंहले दिनहुँ जनावरहरू मारेर खाने गरेको थियो ।\nजनावरहरूले सिंहकहाँ दिनको एक–एक गरेर जाने कुरा गरे ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81409/size6/ebaeb54da24229fafaf409f97a111c87.jpg","text":"यो कुरा सुनेर सिंह खुसी भयो ।\nजनावरहरू पालो–पालो जान थाले ।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81410/size6/265c9caacece28e6ba247405cc6863bf.jpg","text":"एकदिन खरायोको पालो आयो ।\nखरायो ढिलो गयो ।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81411/size6/bf94ff9d86bad764ec551b10b983be57.jpg","text":"सिंह भोकले रिसायो ।\nसिंहले किन ढिलो आएको भनेर सोध्यो ।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81412/size6/ea0d798adef4d52ba4d6ea0d7fdce63c.jpg","text":"खरायोले भन्यो– “मलाई बाटोमा अर्को सिंहले खान आयो”।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81413/size6/c8506323a9d9f5f82c5bb1f382436c01.jpg","text":"यो कुरा सुनेर सिंह धेरै रिसायो ।\nसिंहले खरायोलाई अर्को सिंह देखा भन्यो ।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81414/size6/b27c3342d7240e2de3ed8e1e5e5cac91.jpg","text":"खरायोले सिंहलाई इनारमा लिएर गयो ।\nसिंहले इनारमा हेऱ्यो ।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/95963/size6/0f0ae32d890382c07abb03be38fc435b.jpg","text":"सिंहले इनारमा अर्को सिंह देखेर\nहाम फाल्यो । उ डुबेर मऱ्यो ।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/81416/size6/2be2be5724418859a5ff2781fc5d36d2.jpg","text":"12/12","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":111}}